{"tid":1215620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《愛回家》演員痛心流血衝突事件 Anita急刪靚相 感慨江湖無可奈何","createTime":"2019-06-13T07:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T03:49:08.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"358f2b91c7face545d209c7118b0829d583478cb","tid":1215620,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:43:47.000Z","msg":"最近《逃犯條例》修定引起社會極大爭議，昨日（6月12日）民陣發起全港大規模罷工罷課，不少學校和公司有響應，大批市民集結於金鐘政府總部外和立法會大樓附近，希望政府能撤回《逃犯條例》修定。期間市民與警方發生激烈衝突，警方將事件定性為「騷亂」，又稱使用暴力的示威者為「暴徒」，警方表示在騷亂期出動過的武器包括警棍、胡椒噴劑、布袋彈、橡膠彈及手擲催淚彈。昨日的示威活動引起全港關注，有不少藝人勇於表態撐香港人，希望大家平安，特別是《愛回家》一眾演員非常有愛，如「細龍太」陳偉琪、「Anita」梁茵和「歸蜀明」繆家慶。<br />\n<br />\n陳偉琪連續發了兩個黑底白字的Ig story ，「Stay safe please HK」，又稱「本想post些關於工作的照片。現在沒有心情了。只希望大家平安。」不少網友看完後都對陳偉琪大為讚賞，稱她身為TVB藝人亦勇於發聲，對比其他還在上傳吃喝玩樂動態的藝人好得多。更有網友因此封陳偉琪為「女神」，「多謝細龍太關心香港，希望多啲係幕前見到您」、「即刻愛上佢」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2375000/2375656/fddg_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2375000%2F2375656%2Ffddg_600.jpg&h=47584db2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2375000/2375656/eeee_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2375000%2F2375656%2Feeee_600.jpg&h=fa8781a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而梁茵昨晚原本上載一張塗防曬乳的靚靚自拍照，後來被網友留言斥責，後來她急急刪相，並上傳《倚天屠龍記》周芷若哀傷留涙的劇照，暗有所指地説：「天在哭泣，我抬頭良久，再也掩蓋不了，藏於心底的傷痛，我沒有放聲，亦不想被誤作懦弱。清醒的我沒有歇斯底里，任由水滴沖刷我的妝容，你沒有卸去裝甲，何解此刻我們竟成對立。我們四目交投，無言以對，哨響不斷，煙霧四起，催淚的不是因爲你們無情，而是我們各處一方，慨嘆人在江湖種種的無可奈何。」至於繆家慶則相當直接地上傳兩張黑色圖片，鼓勵香港人：「天佑不了我們，傷害，傷心。堅持，奮鬥。」、「這是持久戰：沉住力氣，繼續。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2375000/2375656/61821968_452580515504117_3036728709840945748_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2375000%2F2375656%2F61821968_452580515504117_3036728709840945748_n_600.jpg&h=aa66eecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2375000/2375656/ddd_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2375000%2F2375656%2Fddd_600.jpg&h=bfe70c15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2375000/2375656/q_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2375000%2F2375656%2Fq_1024.jpg&h=73170ca2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2375656/%E3%80%8A%E6%84%9B%E5%9B%9E%E5%AE%B6%E3%80%8B%E6%BC%94%E5%93%A1%E7%97%9B%E5%BF%83%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%80%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%20Anita%E6%80%A5%E5%88%AA%E9%9D%9A%E7%9B%B8%20%E6%84%9F%E6%85%A8%E6%B1%9F%E6%B9%96%E7%84%A1%E5%8F%AF%E5%A5%88%E4%BD%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2375656%2F%25E3%2580%258A%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E3%2580%258B%25E6%25BC%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%2597%259B%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%25B5%2581%25E8%25A1%2580%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%2520Anita%25E6%2580%25A5%25E5%2588%25AA%25E9%259D%259A%25E7%259B%25B8%2520%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%2585%25A8%25E6%25B1%259F%25E6%25B9%2596%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%25A5%2588%25E4%25BD%2595&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=4e2d879f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2375656/%E3%80%8A%E6%84%9B%E5%9B%9E%E5%AE%B6%E3%80%8B%E6%BC%94%E5%93%A1%E7%97%9B%E5%BF%83%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%80%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%20Anita%E6%80%A5%E5%88%AA%E9%9D%9A%E7%9B%B8%20%E6%84%9F%E6%85%A8%E6%B1%9F%E6%B9%96%E7%84%A1%E5%8F%AF%E5%A5%88%E4%BD%95</a>"},{"pid":"78feb0445a1690fba38d8d79914155f432368294","tid":1215620,"uid":259530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:49:08.000Z","msg":"愛回家朱凌凌細佬以英文發表撐林鄭<br />\n<br />\n把火，見到有學生撐送中，多圖（識英文先好入）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1211143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1211143</a>"}]}